lead_paragraph: With his roster down to eight healthy scholarship players, Arizona coach Sean Miller knew one of his freshmen would have to step up during the Continental Las Vegas Invitational.

headline.print_headline: Markkanen Helps No. 8 Arizona Hold Off Santa Clara, 69-61
